%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Old%20man%20can't%20even%20...'%3A%20Trump%20mocked%20for%20'empty%20seats'%20at%20rally%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719196395000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111217454%2Cimgsize-945692.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fold-man-cant-even-trump-mocked-for-empty-seats-at-pennsylvania-rally%2Farticleshow%2F111217387.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump%20faced%20ridicule%20on%20social%20media%20for%20his%20rally%20at%20Temple%20University's%20Liacouras%20Center%2C%20which%20had%20empty%20seats.%20Chris%20Jackson%20and%20Peter%20Henlein%20criticized%20the%20low%20attendance%20at%20the%20event.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20WORLD%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gunmen%20Attack%20Churches%2C%20Synagogues%20In%20Russia%3B%20Cops%2C%20Priest%20Among%2015%20Killed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAt%20least%2015%20people%2C%20including%20policemen%20and%20a%20priest%2C%20were%20killed%20and%20several%20others%20injured%20after%20unidentified%20gunmen%20opened%20fire%20at%20synagogues%2C%20churches%2C%20and%20a%20police%20post%20in%20Russia's%20North%20Caucasus%20region%20of%20Dagestan%20on%20Sunday%2C%20the%20region's%20governor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20simultaneous%20attacks%20occurred%20in%20Dagestan's%20largest%20city%20of%20Makhachkala%20and%20in%20the%20coastal%20city%20of%20Derbent%20with%20Governor%20Sergei%20Melikov%20calling%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bterrorist%20attack%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20that%20the%20police%20personnel%20had%20killed%20four%20gunmen%20in%20Makhachkala%20and%20two%20in%20Derbent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMelikov%20said%20that%20among%20the%20dead%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20police%20officers%2C%20were%20several%20civilians%2C%20including%20an%20Orthodox%20priest%20who%20had%20