%20team.%20However%2C%20there%20was%20no%20mention%20of%20the%20players%20being%20discarded%20from%20all%20three%20formats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20the%20fourth%20condition%20is%20concerned%2C%20there%20will%20be%20a%20separate%20team%20in%20Test%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELastly%2C%20Gambhir%20will%20start%20preparing%20a%20roadmap%20for%20the%202027%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20from%20the%20get-go.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20is%20pretty%20clear%20if%20the%20four%20senior%20players%20--%20Virat%2C%20Rohit%2C%20Jadeja%20and%20Shami%20--%20will%20be%20dropped%20from%20the%20team%20if%20they%20don't%20perform%20in%20the%202025%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%20the%20question%20remains%20if%20the%20players%20will%20continue%20to%20play%20red%20ball%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKohli%20and%20Rohit's%20future%20has%20already%20been%20uncertain%2C%20and%20with%20Gambhir's%20name%20linked%20with%20the%20India%20head%20coach%20job%2C%20it%20won't%20be%20a%20big%20surprise%20that%20the%20two%20veterans%20could%20be%20overlooked%20for%20selection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20worth%20noting%20that%20India%20could%20feature%20in%20the%20World%20Test%20Championship%20final%20next%20year.%20There%20could%20be%20a%20possibility%20of%20them%20getting%20dropped%20if%20India%20don't%20win%20the%20Test%20mace%20next%20time%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20have%20lost%20the%20last%20two%20World%20Test%20Championship%20finals%20to%20New%20Zealand%20(2021)%20and%20Australia%20(2023)%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719195600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fp8nlq3ug_virat-kohli-rohit-sharma-gautam-gambhir_625x300_23_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgautam-gambhir-sets-bold-virat-kohli-rohit-sharma-champions-trophy-condition-for-india-coach-job-report-5953515%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gautam%20Gambhir%20was%20interviewed%20last%20week%20by%20BCCI's%20Cricket%20Advisory%20Co