0and%20Helaena%20attend%20the%20procession%20behind%20Jaehaerys'%20body.%3Cp%3ETheo%20Whitman%2FHBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPalmer%20Haasch%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThere%20are%20a%20few%20really%20important%20reactions%20here%3A%20Alicent%20feels%20like%20she's%20being%20divinely%20punished%2C%20Helaena%20is%20utterly%20grief-stricken%2C%20Rhaenyra%20is%20aghast%20that%20she's%20being%20blamed%2C%20and%20Otto%20knows%20that%20this%20is%20the%20biggest%20political%20gift%20his%20side%20will%20probably%20ever%20see.%20And%20he's%20right!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECaralynn%20Matassa%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20And%20Aegon%20%E2%80%94%20just%20utterly%20wrecked.%20Any%20intention%20he%20had%20to%20try%20to%20be%20a%20good%20king%20is%20entirely%20wiped%20away%20here%20in%20favor%20of%20vengeance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPalmer%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20think%20it's%20interesting%2C%20because%20you%20really%20don't%20get%20the%20impression%20that%20Aegon%20cares%20too%20much%20about%20his%20children%20until%20he%20starts%20to%20see%20Jaehaerys%20as%20a%20viable%20heir.%20Even%20though%20he%20didn't%20want%20the%20throne%20himself%2C%20he%20too%20has%20become%20power-drunk%20and%20wants%20to%20continue%20his%20legacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEammon%20Jacobs%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPhia%20Saban's%20performance%20during%20that%20procession%20scene%20is%20so%20haunting.%20She's%20doing%20so%20much%20without%20needing%20to%20wail%20lines%20of%20over-the-top%20predictable%20dialogue.%20It's%20clear%20that%20Helaena%20is%20tapping%20into%20%3Cem%3Esomething%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebigger%20too%2C%20just%20with%20the%20focus%20on%20the%20seeds%2Fleaves%20blowing%20in%20the%20wind%20and%20her%20frantic%20facial%20expressions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAyomikun%20Adekaiyero%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20series%20does%20a%20great%20job%20of%20showing%20how%20this%20toxic%20masculinity%20among%20the%20men%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20Aegon%2C%20Daemon%2C%20and%20Criston%20%E2%80%94%20escalates%20this%20conflict.%20Aegon%20doesn't%20really%20care%20about%20Jaehaerys%3B%20he%20is%20terrified%20at%20looking%20weak%2C%20which%20also%20isn't%20his%20fault%2C%20considering%20he%20has%20been%20raised%20to%20be%20this%20great%20king.%20Tom%20Glynn-Carney%20really%20has%20one%20of%20the%20best%20performances%20in%20this%20episode.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20on%20the%20toxic%20masculinity%20point%2C%20it's%20interesting%20to%20see%20how%20the%20harm%20of%20this%20conflict%20so%20far%20is%20mostly%20affecting%20the%20women.%20Rhaenyra%20is%20blamed%20for%20a%20murder%20she%20didn't%20order%2C%20Alicent%20and%20Helaena%20are%20forced%20to%20perform%20for%20the%20royal%20family%20during%20their%20grief%20while%20the%20men%20plot%20and%20create%20more%20chaos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPalmer%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20This%20is%20also%20really%20the%20moment%20where%20we%20realize%20how%20much%20of%20a%20curse%20Helaena%20being%20a%20dreamer%20is.%20She%20can%20foreshadow%20the%20death%20of%20her%20own%20son%2C%20but%20she%20doesn't%20realize%20it%20and%20can't%20prevent%20it.%20The%20entire%20funeral%20procession%20should%20also%20satiate%20everyone%20who%20didn't%20think%20the%20death%20was%20horrifying%20enough%20%E2%80%94%20I%20think%20seeing%20little%20Jaehaerys%2C%20with%20his%20neck%20stitched%2C%20valorized%20like%20a%20martyr%20in%20the%20streets%20is%20infinitely%20worse%20than%20whatever%20else%20we%20could%20have%20gotten%20out%20of%20Blood%20and%20Cheese.%20Phia's%20performance%20here%20heightens%20the%20entire%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECaralynn%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Phia%20and%20Tom%20were%20both%20such%20standouts%20in%20this%20episode!%20The%20way%20the%20procession%20was%20staged%20and%20filmed%20was%20also%20gorgeous%20and%20so%20evocative.%20The%20closeup%20on%20little%20Jaehaerys'%20sewn-on%20head%20almost%20made%20me%20puke.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPalmer%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20also%20want%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20conversation%20between%20Alicent%20and%20Helaena%20right%20before%20the%20funeral%20procession%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20a%20huge%20insight%20into%20Alicent%20as%20a%20mother.%20For%20the%20most%20part%2C%20I've%20gotten%20the%20impression%20that%20the%20moments%20where%20she's%20protecting%20her%20children%20are%20also%20deep%20political%20moves%2C%20like%20when%20she%20demanded%20Lucerys'%20eye%20at%20Driftmark%20in%20season%20one.%20But%20in%20this%20moment%2C%20she%20is%20truly%20throwing%20Helaena%20to%20the%20wolves%2C%20and%20knows%20it.%20Olivia%20manages%20to%20elucidate%20this%20tension%20between%20protecting%20her%20daughter%20from%20scrutiny%20and%20making%20the%20savvy%20political%20choice%2C%20but%20obviously%2C%20we%20know%20where%20Alicent%20lands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECaralynn%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I've%20never%20had%20less%20sympathy%20for%20Alicent%20than%20in%20this%20episode.%20You%20can%20see%20her%20struggling%20with%20this%20choice%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that's%20all%20thanks%20to%20Olivia's%20meticulous%20performance%20%E2%80%94%20but%20she%20makes%20the%20wrong%20choice%20at%20literally%20every%20opportunity%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPalmer%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20do%20think%20that%20she%20is%20unfortunately%20pretty%20on%20the%20nose%20when%20she%20says%20that%20she's%20being%20punished%20by%20the%20gods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAyomikun%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20haven't%20read%20the%20books%2C%20and%20maybe%20I'm%20reading%20into%20the%20procession%20too%20much%2C%20but%20I%20feel%20like%20there%20was%20so%20much%20foreshadowing%20that%20there%20is%20worse%20to%20come.%20The%20flowers%20of%20the%20funeral%20fall%20down%20like%20ash%2C%20terrifying%20Helaena.%20The%20people%20of%20the%20city%20reach%20out%20as%20if%20they%20are%20also%20in%20pain.%20So%20far%2C%20the%20casualties%20have%20all%20been%20kept%20to%20the%20royal%20family%20but%20there%20is%20a%20great%20sense%20that%20this%20is%20going%20to%20go%20really%20badly%20for%20%3Cem%3Eeveryone%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEammon%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20That's%20a%20constant%20theme%20in%20the%20franchise%2C%20really%20%E2%80%94%20the%20smallfolk%20always%20pay%20for%20the%20actions%20of%20the%20upper%20class.%20We%20saw%20that%20back%20in%20season%20one%20when%20Rhaenys%20broke%20out%20of%20the%20Dragonpit%20and%20squished%20people%20watching%20the%20coronation!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cc47f1af-269a-488c-9c0c-4e5eee3c1a87%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon't%20ignore%20the%20smallfolk%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221707%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kieran%20Bew%2C%20Ellora%20Torchia%20in%20House%20of%20the%20Drago%2C%20Season%202%20-%20Episode%202%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6678667e40cf2af6e4f4de01%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20get%20it%2C%20Hugh%20Hammer%20is%20going%20to%20be%20important%20soon.%3Cp%3EOllie%20Upton%2FHBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECaralynn%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Speaking%20of%20squished%20people%2C%20we%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20smallfolk%20scenes%20scattered%20throughout%20the%20episode.%20But%20the%20most%20effective%20for%20me%20was%20that%20mom%20who%20saw%20her%20dead%20ratcatcher%20son%20strung%20up.%20And%20the%20dog%20giving%20that%20small%20whine%20when%20he%20saw%20Cheese%20dead!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPalmer%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Thank%20god%20the%20dog%20is%20safe!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAyomikun%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20hanging%20scene%20really%20highlights%20how%20much%20Aegon%20messed%20up%20more%20than%20Otto's%20tirade.%20The%20smallfolk%20don't%20really%20know%20the%20ins-and-outs%20of%20what's%20going%20on%2C%20but%20they%20know%20their%20king%20has%20just%20murdered%20the%20lowest%20of%20their%20servants%2C%20most%20of%20whom%20were%20completely%20innocent.%20They%20likely%20will%20trust%20Aegon%20less%20than%20Rhaenyra%2C%20who%20kept%20the%20conflict%20to%20just%20the%20royals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPalmer%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20To%20be%20fair%2C%20Aegon%20is%20barely%20still%20winning%20the%20PR%20war%20because%20everyone%20thinks%20Rhaenyra%20killed%20a%20child.%20But%20yeah%2C%20ultimately%2C%20I%20agree%20with%20you%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20funny%20because%20everyone%20was%20lauding%20him%20as%20a%20wealth%20redistribution%20icon%20in%20the%20last%20episode.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAegon%20giveth%20sheep.....%20he%20taketh%20away%20sheep.....%20he%20slays%20rat%20men.......%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEammon%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20do%20think%20that%20even%20in%20the%20first%20two%20episodes%2C%20the%20writers%20are%20trying%20to%20show%20the%20war%20from%20the%20smallfolk's%20perspective%20%E2%80%94%20maybe%20more%20than%20%26quot%3BGame%20of%20Thrones.%26quot%3B%20We%20had%20the%20sheep%2Fdragon%20debate%20last%20week%2C%20and%20now%20we've%20got%20the%20elimination%20of%20the%20ratcatchers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPalmer%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20have%20mixed%20feelings%20about%20how%20the%20series%20handles%20this%2C%20because%2C%20on%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20I%20think%20that%20it's%20hugely%20important%20for%20the%20show%20to%20contextualize%20the%20war%20within%20the%20actual%20population%20of%20Westeros%20in%20order%20to%20convey%20the%20scope.%20But%20I%20also%20think%20that%20it's%20a%20bit%20halfhearted%20when%20%E2%80%94%20ratcatcher%20mother%20aside%20%E2%80%94%20the%20smallfolk%20we%20interact%20with%20the%20most%20in%20the%20show%20are%20all%20like%2C%20hugely%20important%20characters%20down%20the%20line.%20They're%20not%20truly%20the%20everyman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECaralynn%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%2C%20for%20one%2C%20found%20it%20hard%20to%20care%20about%20the%20scene%20with%20Hugh's%20family%20because%20it%20just%20felt%20so%20much%20like%20a%20set-up%20for%20his%20eventual%20More%20Important%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEammon%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Tha