e%20Sea%20Snake%20is%20to%20make%20your%20fortune.%20Had%20I%20such%20a%20chance%2C%20I%20would%20leap%20at%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Addam%20tells%20Alyn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlyn%20reminds%20his%20brother%20that%20there's%20a%20real%2C%20impending%20war.%20Addam%20thinks%20that%20Corlys%20owes%20Alyn%20(presumably%20for%20saving%20his%20life)%2C%20but%20then%20cryptically%20adds%20that%20Corlys%20owes%20both%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20writers%20are%20telegraphing%20pretty%20hard%20that%20these%20are%20characters%20we'll%20see%20again%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0here's%20what%20happens%20to%20them%20in%20%26quot%3BFire%20and%20Blood.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMajor%20potential%20show%20spoilers%20ahead.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Steve%20Toussaint%20as%20Corlys%20Velaryon%20in%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6596e3d31c5c7b8c9a0df275%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESteve%20Toussaint%20as%20Corlys%20Velaryon%20in%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EHBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2294a62b6d-7842-4e35-b979-1d1a9800e2c7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAddam%20of%20Hull%20becomes%20a%20dragon%20rider%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20events%20of%20%26quot%3BFire%20and%20Blood%2C%26quot%3B%20Jaecaerys%20Velaryon%20promises%20wealth%20to%20any%20man%20able%20to%20claim%20a%20dragon.%20Addam%20successfully%20claims%20Seasmoke%2C%20the%20former%20dragon%20of%20Laenor%20Velaryon%2C%20Rhaenyra's%20husband.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20likely%20the%20show%20will%20go%20this%20route%20too%3B%20in%20episode%20two%2C%20Addam%20observes%20a%20pale%20dragon%20resembling%20Seasmoke%20flying%20above%20him%20as%20he%20picks%20up%20a%20crab%20on%20the%20beach.%20Pretty%20strong%20foreshadowing!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20book%2C%20both%20Alyn%20and%20A