href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-couple-moved-bali-slow-life-build-house-start-family-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emoved%20to%20Bali%3C%2Fa%3E%20two%20years%20ago%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ein%20July%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20grew%20up%20in%20Malaysia%20and%20started%20my%20career%20working%20in%20fashion%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-old-house-renovation-before-after-japandi-kuala-lumpur-malaysia-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKuala%20Lumpur%3C%2Fa%3E.%20While%20living%20in%20the%20capital%2C%20I%20met%20Steve%2C%20who%20had%20moved%20over%20from%20Sydney%20to%20work%20in%20education%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20dating%20for%20a%20month%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20live%20together.%20We%20started%20in%20his%20apartment%20and%20found%20a%20better-located%20one-bedroom%20service%20apartment%20six%20months%20later.%20We%20were%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20city%2C%20near%20the%20botanical%20garden%2C%20and%20happily%20called%20it%20home%20for%20six%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20when%20I%20suggested%20the%20move%20to%20Bali.%20I%20had%20been%20running%20my%20own%20digital%20content%20business%20on%20the%20side%20for%208%20years%20and%20working%20at%20a%20women's%20retreat%20company.%20I've%20always%20been%20passionate%20about%20empowering%20women%2C%20and%20those%20retreats%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eopened%20up%20a%20whole%20new%20world%20to%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wanted%20to%20meet%20like-minded%20women%20and%20build%20a%20community%20with%20coaches%20who%20I%20could%20learn%20from.%20I%20wanted%20a%20new%20challenge%2C%20and%20Bali%20seemed%20like%20a%20place%20ripe%20with%20creative%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Findonesia-bali-tourist-mistake-travel-guide-local-tips-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrawn%20to%20Bali%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20it%20was%20an%20international%20hub%20between%20Kuala%20Lumpur%20and%20Sydney%2C%20where%20our%20families%20lived.%20We%20also%20really%20wanted%20to%20connect%20with%20nature%2C%20especially%20after%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20Steve%20was%20also%20looking%20to%20make%20a%20career%20switch%2C%20it%20felt%20like%20the%20right%20time%20for%20us%20to%20start%20the%20next%20phase%20of%20our%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20we%20took%20the%20plunge.%20Looking%20back%2C%20it%20was%20a%20quick%20process%3A%20We%20made%20the%20decision%20in%20January%202022%2C%20and%20six%20months%20later%2C%20we%20were%20in%20Bali.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20possibilities%20ahead%20of%20us%20felt%20boundless%2C%20and%20we%20couldn't%20wait%20to%20explore%20new%20sides%20of%20ourselves.%20In%20hindsight%2C%20it%20took%20us%20longer%20to%20find%20our%20footing%20than%20we%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2246e43255-84e1-4099-ad26-6d94ee864a15%5C%22%3EWe%20jumped%20in%20and%20tried%20to%20learn%20how%20things%20worked%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bureaucratic%20stuff%20was%20tough%2C%20and%20we%20soon%20realized%20there%20was%20no%20how-to%20manual.%20We%20ended%20up%20learning%20everything%20the%20hard%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20we%20were%20used%20to%20having%20our%20bill%20payments%20automated.%20In%20Bali%2C%20we%20paid%20them%20in%20person%20for%20a%20few%20months%20before%20we%20finally%20learned%20how%20to%20do%20it%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20missed%20the%20convenience%20of%20our%20service%20apartment%2C%20which%20had%20an%20amazing%20gym%20and%20easy%20access%20to%20public%20transport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Australia%2C%20it's%20easy%20to%20walk%20everywhere.%20In%20Malaysia%2C%20we%20could%20also%20jump%20into%20a%20car%2C%20but%20here%2C%20although%20it%20looks%20like%20you%20can%20walk%20to%20your%20destination%2C%20there%20are%20hardly%20any%20sidewalks.%20You%20have%20to%20hop%20on%20a%20motorbike%20to%20get%20around%2C%20and%20it%20took%20us%2010%20months%20be