20few%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20do%2C%20however%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-things-at-costco-family-of-five-grocery-list-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebatch%20shop%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20work%20out%20how%20many%20of%20each%20thing%20we%20get%20through%20a%20week%20for%20perishables%20and%20a%20month%20for%20non-perishables%20and%20buy%20enough%20at%20once.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20made%20easier%20because%20I%20eat%20the%20same%20meal%20for%20as%20many%20weeks%20as%20I%20can%20stomach.%20So%20far%2C%20my%20limit%20has%20been%20five%20weeks%20of%20salmorejo%20%E2%80%94%20a%20cold%20Spanish%20soup%2C%20similar%20to%20gazpacho.%20The%20soup%20hits%20all%20the%20main%20food%20groups%20as%20it's%20served%20with%20croutons%2C%20chopped%20veggies%2C%20jamon%2C%20and%20a%20crumbled%20boiled%20egg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2225adee6a-2e76-40f1-82c0-3ccf170d0035%5C%22%3EI%20do%20my%20admin%20in%20the%20playground%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spend%20almost%202%20hours%20a%20day%20watching%20my%20two%20sons%20in%20the%20playground%20after%20school.%20That%20was%20dead%20time%20until%20I%20started%20taking%20my%20little%20Chromebook%20with%20me%20and%20working.%20I%20leave%20certain%20kinds%20of%20tasks%20specifically%20for%20this%20extra%20slot%20I've%20magicked%20into%20my%20day%2C%20like%20admin%20and%20emailing.%20When%20they're%20happily%20playing%20with%20friends%2C%20I%20often%20get%20a%20stretch%20of%20time%20long%20enough%20to%20write%20marketing%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20on%20the%20walk%20back%20from%20dropping%20off%20the%20kids%20or%20picking%20them%20up%20from%20school%2C%20I%20send%20myself%20voice%20notes%20that%20I%20can%20later%20transcribe%20by%20AI%20and%20turn%20into%20material.%20It's%20a%20great%20time%20for%20listening%20to%20podcasts%20relevant%20to%20my%20business%20too.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWalking%20has%20another%20plus%3A%20it%20can%20enhance%20creativity.%20That's%20what%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudy-walks-make-you-more-creative-2014-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStanford%20University%20researchers%20found%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20study%20published%20in%202014%20in%20the%20Journal%20of%20Experimental%20Psychology.%20The%20participants%20who%20went%20for%20walks%20saw%20an%2081%25%20increase%20in%20tests%20measuring%20divergent%20thinking%2C%20a%20thought%20process%20associated%20with%20creativity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226652f3ed-5288-42dc-a785-cd332a8df80b%5C%22%3EI%20make%20use%20of%20sleepless%20nights%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20children%20are%206%20and%209%20but%20they%20still%20regularly%20wake%20me%20in%20the%20night%20for%20anything%20from%20going%20to%20the%20bathroom%20to%20throwing%20up.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20if%20I%20couldn't%20get%20back%20to%20sleep%2C%20I'd%20just%20lie%20there%2C%20restless%20and%20awake%2C%20until%20the%20alarm.%20Now%20I%20get%20up%20and%20work%20instead.%20Thanks%20to%20some%20of%20these%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstay-at-home-mom-works-part-time-morning-routine-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epre-dawn%20wakeups%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20have%20built%20a%20website%2C%20launched%20my%20business%2C%20and%20regularly%20beat%20deadlines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDon't%20get%20me%20wrong%20%E2%80%94%20I'd%20never%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsuccessful-people-who-wake-up-early-before-6-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewake%20up%20that%20early%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20purpose%2C%20but%20making%20the%20most%20of%20it%20has%20been%20productive.%20I%20usually%20get%20a%20full%20night's%20sleep%20the%20next%20night%20because%20I%20have%20to%20go%20to%20bed%20early%20to%20compensate.%20But%20it's%20not%20like%20I'm%20sacrificing%20my%20evening%20social%20life%20because%20I%20don't%20have%20one%20as%20a%20single%20mother%20anyway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2245b7819a-1136-4a64-92a3-2240f8eff