0Terrorism%20Shouldn't%20Be%20Tolerated%3A%20Minister%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20missions%20in%20Canadian%20capital%20Ottawa%20and%20Toronto%20city%20on%20Sunday%20marked%20the%2039th%20anniversary%20of%20the%201985%20Kanishka%20bombing%20in%20which%20329%20persons%2C%20including%2086%20children%2C%20on%20board%20an%20Air%20India%20lost%20their%20lives%20in%20one%20of%20the%20most%20heinous%20terror-related%20air%20disasters%20in%20the%20history%20of%20civil%20aviation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHigh%20Commissioner%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20Verma%20paid%20homage%20to%20the%20victims%20of%20Air%20India%20flight%20182%20Kanishka%20on%20the%2039th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bcowardly%20terrorist%20bombing%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20High%20Commission%20in%20Ottawa%20posted%20on%20X%20along%20with%20a%20series%20of%20photographs%20from%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20gathering%2C%20Mr%20Verma%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%20government%20in%20the%20world%20should%20overlook%20the%20threat%20of%20terrorism%20emanating%20from%20its%20territories%20for%20political%20gains.%20Human%20lives%20are%20much%20more%20important%20than%20the%20transitory%20political%20interests.%20All%20terrorist%20activities%20should%20be%20met%20with%20exemplary%20legal%20and%20social%20actions%2C%20before%20they%20start%20harming%20the%20larger%20humanity.%20Governments%2C%20security%20agencies%2C%20and%20international%20organisations%20must%20work%20in%20concert%20to%20dismantle%20terrorist%20networks%2C%20disrupt%20their%20financing%2C%20and%20counter%20their%20twisted%20ideologies.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EHigh%20Commissioner%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20Verma%20paid%20homage%20to%20the%20victims%20of%20Air%20India%20flight%20182%20Kanishka%20in%20Ottawa%20today%20on%20the%2039th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20cowardly%20terrorist%20bombing%20in%20which%20329%20innocent%20victims%20including%2086%20children%2C%20lost%20their%20lives.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAddressing%20the%20gathering%2C%20High%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FiL4bpg86vh%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FiL4bpg86vh%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20India%20in%20Canada%20(%40HCI_Ottawa)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHCI_Ottawa%2Fstatus%2F1804939868935467162%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2023%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EFamily%20members%20and%20friends%20of%20the%20victims%2C%20Canadian%20government%20officials%2C%20including%20Royal%20Canadian%20Mounted%20Police%20Assistant%20Commissioner%2C%20Ireland%20envoy%20and%20more%20than%20150%20members%20of%20the%20Indo-Canadian%20community%20attended%20the%20solemn%20occasion%2C%20the%20High%20Commission%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20shares%20the%20sorrow%20and%20pain%20of%20the%20victims'%20near%20%26amp%3B%20dear%20ones.%20India%20stands%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20countering%20the%20menace%20of%20terrorism%20and%20works%20closely%20with%20all%20nations%20to%20tackle%20this%20global%20threat%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Montreal-New%20Delhi%20Air%20India%20'Kanishka'%20Flight%20182%20exploded%2045%20minutes%20before%20it%20was%20supposed%20to%20land%20at%20London's%20Heathrow%20Airport%20on%20June%2023%2C%201985%2C%20killing%20all%20329%20people%20on%20board%2C%20most%20of%20them%20Canadians%20of%20Indian%20descent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bombing%20was%20blamed%20on%20Sikh%20separatists%20in%20retaliation%20to%20'Operation%20Bluestar'%20to%20flush%20out%20separatists%20from%20the%20Golden%20Temple%20in%201984.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20mission%20in%20Toronto%20also%20marked%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConsul%20General%20Siddhartha%20Nath%20laid%20a%20wreath%20at%20the%20Air%20India%20182%20memorial%2C%20Humber%20Park%2C%20Etobicoke%20in%20solemn%20remembrance%20of%20the%20329%20victims%20