%20thoughts%20are%20with%20their%20families.%20The%20anniversary%20is%20a%20reminder%20why%20terrorism%20should%20never%20be%20tolerated%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20the%20Canadian%20police%20said%20the%20investigations%20into%20the%20bombing%20of%20the%20Air%20India%20Flight%20182%20remain%20%26quot%3Bactive%20and%20ongoing%26quot%3B%2C%20terming%20it%20the%20%26quot%3Blongest%26quot%3B%20and%20one%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bmost%20complex%20domestic%20terrorism%26quot%3B%20probes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20Royal%20Canadian%20Mounted%20Police%20(RCMP)%20Assistant%20Commissioner%20David%20Teboul%20called%20the%20bombing%20the%20%26quot%3Bgreatest%20terror-related%20loss%20of%20life%20involving%20and%20affecting%20Canadians%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20country's%20history%20as%20he%20offered%20%26quot%3Bdeepest%20sympathies%2C%20understanding%20and%20support%20to%20the%20families%20of%20the%20victims%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Air%20India%20investigation%20is%20the%20longest%20and%20certainly%20one%20of%20the%20most%20complex%20domestic%20terrorism%20investigations%20that%20the%20RCMP%20has%20undertaken%20in%20our%20history%2C%26quot%3B%20Teboul%20said.%20%26quot%3BOur%20investigative%20efforts%20remain%20active%20and%20ongoing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719174060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F9ol7j6mg_kanishka-bombings-victim_625x300_24_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkanishka-bombing-a-reminder-why-terrorism-shouldnt-be-tolerated-s-jaishankar-5954463%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20missions%20in%20Canadian%20capital%20Ottawa%20and%20Toronto%20city%20on%20Sunday%20marked%20the%2039th%20anni