%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESaudi%20Arabia%20said%20Sunday%20that%20more%20than%201%2C300%20faithful%20died%20during%20the%20hajj%20pilgrimage%20which%20took%20place%20during%20intense%20heat%20and%20that%20most%20of%20them%20who%20died%20did%20not%20have%20official%20permits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRegrettably%2C%20the%20number%20of%20mortalities%20reached%201%2C301%2C%20with%2083%20percent%20being%20unauthorised%20to%20perform%20hajj%20and%20having%20walked%20long%20distances%20under%20direct%20sunlight%2C%20without%20adequate%20shelter%20or%20comfort%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20Saudi%20Press%20Agency%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20AFP%20tally%20last%20week%2C%20based%20on%20official%20statements%20and%20reports%20from%20diplomats%20involved%20in%20their%20countries'%20responses%2C%20put%20the%20count%20at%20more%20than%201%2C100.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dead%20came%20from%20more%20than%2010%20countries%20stretching%20from%20the%20United%20States%20to%20Indonesia%2C%20and%20some%20governments%20are%20continuing%20to%20update%20their%20totals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArab%20diplomats%20told%20AFP%20last%20week%20that%20Egyptians%20accounted%20for%20658%20deaths%20--%20630%20of%20them%20unregistered%20pilgrims.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20diplomats%20said%20the%20cause%20of%20death%20in%20most%20cases%20was%20heat-related.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETemperatures%20in%20Mecca%20this%20year%20climbed%20as%20high%20as%2051.8%20degrees%20Celsius%20(125%20degrees%20Fahrenheit)%2C%20according%20to%20Saudi%20Arabia's%20national%20meteorological%20centre.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERiyadh%20had%20not%20publicly%20commented%20on%20the%20deaths%20or%20provided%20its%20own%20count%20until%20Sunday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20however%2C%20a%20senior%20Saudi%20official%20gave%20AFP%20a%20partial%20count%20of%20577%20deaths%20for%20the%20two%20busiest%20days%20of%20hajj%3A%20June%2015%2C%20when%20pilgrims%20gathered%20for%20hours%20of%20prayers%20in%20the%20blazing%20sun%20on%20Mount%20Arafat%2C%20and%20June%2016%2C%20when%20they%20participated%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bstoning%20of%20the%20devil%26quot%3B%20ritual%20in%20Mina.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20also%20defended%20Riyadh's%20response%2C%20saying%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20state%20did%20not%20fail%2C%20but%20there%20was%20a%20misjudgement%20on%20the%20part%20of%20people%20who%20did%20not%20appreciate%20the%20risks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Heat%20stress'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Saudi%20health%20minister%2C%20Fahd%20Al-Jalajel%2C%20on%20Sunday%20described%20management%20of%20the%20hajj%20this%20year%20as%20%26quot%3Bsuccessful%26quot%3B%2C%20SPA%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20health%20system%20%26quot%3Bprovided%20more%20than%20465%2C000%20specialised%20treatment%20services%2C%20including%20141%2C000%20services%20to%20those%20who%20didn't%20obtain%20official%20authorisation%20to%20perform%20hajj%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20SPA%2C%20which%20summarised%20an%20interview%20he%20gave%20to%20the%20state-affiliated%20Al-Ekhbariya%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJalajel%20did%20not%20specify%20how%20many%20deaths%20Saudi%20officials%20attributed%20to%20heat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20health%20system%20addressed%20numerous%20cases%20of%20heat%20stress%20this%20year%2C%20with%20some%20individuals%20still%20under%20care%2C%26quot%3B%20SPA%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAmong%20the%20deceased%20were%20several%20elderly%20and%20chronically%20ill%20individuals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hajj%20is%20one%20of%20the%20five%20pillars%20of%20Islam%20that%20all%20Muslims%20with%20the%20means%20must%20complete%20at%20least%20once%20in%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaudi%20officials%20have%20said%201.8%20million%20pilgrims%20took%20part%20this%20year%2C%20a%20similar%20number%20to%20last%20year%2C%20and%20that%201.6%20million%20came%20from%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%20several%20years%20the%20mainly%20outdoor%20rituals%20have%20fallen%20during%20the%20sweltering%20Saudi%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20timing%20of%20the%20hajj%20moves%20forward%20about%2011%20days%20each%20year%20in%20the%20Gregorian%20calendar%2C%20meaning%20that%20next%20year%20it%20will%20take%20place%20earlier%20in%20June%2C%20potentially%20in%20cooler%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%202019%20study%20by%20the%20journal%20Geophysical%20Research%20Letters%20said%20because%20of%20climate%20change%2C%20heat%20stress%20for%20hajj%20pilgrims%20will%20exceed%20the%20%26quot%3Bextreme%20danger%20threshold%26quot%3B%20from%202047%20to%202052%20and%202079%20to%202086%2C%20%26quot%3Bwith%20increasing%20frequency%20and%20intensity%20as%20the%20century%20progresses%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EOff-the-books%20hajj%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHajj%20permits%20are%20allocated%20to%20countries%20on%20a%20quota%20system%20and%20distributed%20to%20individuals%20by%20lottery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20for%20those%20who%20can%20obtain%20them%2C%20the%20steep%20costs%20spur%20many%20to%20attempt%20the%20hajj%20without%20a%20permit%2C%20though%20they%20risk%20arrest%20and%20deportation%20if%20caught.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaudi%20authorities%20said%20before%20the%20hajj%20that%20they%20had%20cleared%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20unregistered%20pilgrims%20from%20Mecca.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Saudi%20official%20who%20spoke%20to%20AFP%20on%20Friday%20said%20around%20400%2C000%20unregistered%20pilgrims%20took%20part%2C%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Balmost%20all%20of%20them%20(were)%20from%20one%20nationality%26quot%3B%2C%20an%20apparent%20reference%20to%20Egypt.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20Egyptian%20Prime%20Minister%20Mostafa%20Madbouly%20ordered%2016%20tourism%20companies%20stripped%20of%20their%20licences%20and%20referred%20their%20managers%20to%20the%20public%20prosecutor%20over%20illegal%20pilgrimages%20to%20Mecca%2C%20Egypt's%20cabinet%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20the%20rise%20in%20the%20number%20of%20deaths%20of%20unregistered%20Egyptian%20pilgrims%20stemmed%20from%20some%20companies%20which%20%26quot%3Borganised%20the%20hajj%20programmes%20using%20a%20personal%20visit%20visa%2C%20which%20prevents%20its%20holders%20from%20entering%20Mecca%26quot%3B%20via%20official%20channels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnregistered%20pilgrims%20in%20many%20cases%20did%20not%20have%20access%20to%20amenities%20meant%20to%20make%20the%20pilgrimage%20more%20bearable%2C%20including%20air-conditioned%20tents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnregistered%20Egyptian%20pilgrims%20told%20AFP%20last%20week%20that%20in%20some%20cases%20they%20struggled%20to%20access%20hospitals%20or%20hail%20ambulances%20for%20loved%20ones%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20ended%20up%20dying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719172440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fg68pm4v8_hajj-reuters-1200_625x300_21_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fover-1-300-deaths-during-hajj-due-to-intense-heat-83-pilgrims-unregistered-saudi-5954459%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Saudi%20Arabia%20said%20Sunday%20that%20more%20than%201%2C300%20faithful%20died%20during%20the%20hajj%20pilgrimage%20which%20took%20place%20during%20intense%20heat%20and%20that%20most%20of%20them%20who%20died%20did%20not%20have%20official%20permits.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fover-1-300-deaths-during-hajj-due-to-intense-heat-83-pilgrims-unregistered-saudi-5954459%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fover-1-300-deaths-during-hajj-due-to-intense-heat-83-pilgrims-unr