ealth%20%26quot%3Bassociates%2C%26quot%3B%20motivational%20speakers%2C%20and%2C%20of%20course%2C%20life%20coaches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20range%20of%20reasons%20a%20therapist%20might%20lose%20their%20license%2C%20from%20disclosing%20confidential%20information%20to%20engaging%20in%20inappropriate%20relationships.%20ProPublica's%20analysis%20found%20that%20a%20handful%20of%20therapists%20who%20were%20still%20practicing%20had%20lost%20their%20licenses%20for%20%26quot%3Bserious%20reasons%2C%26quot%3B%20ranging%20from%20drug%20and%20substance%20abuse%20to%20inappropriate%20contact%20with%20patients%20to%20sexual%20exploitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMark%20Steinagel%2C%20a%20director%20in%20the%20Utah%20state%20government%20who%20oversees%20licensing%2C%20told%20the%20outlet%20that%20licensers%20can't%20prevent%20these%20individuals%20from%20doing%20the%20same%20work%20as%20life%20coaches.%20However%2C%20investigators%20do%20try%20to%20watch%20them%20to%20ensure%20they%20don't%20veer%20back%20into%20therapy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Hildebrandt%20case%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.abc4.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fruby-franke-husband-calls-for-more-regulation-on-life-coaches%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einspired%20legislation%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Utah%20to%20regulate%20the%20life%20coaching%20industry.%20The%20bill%20is%20now%20undergoing%20legislative%20review.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20prospective%20patients%20should%20research%20before%20choosing%20a%20life%20coach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCoaching%20is%20not%20therapy%20and%20I%20don't%20want%20it%20to%20be%20confused%20in%20any%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20life%20coach%20Suzanne%20Culberg%20said%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9HDNWeQKUiU%26t%3D1100s%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterview%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20ethics%20of%20life%20coaching%20with%20the%20YouTuber%20Danielle%20Ryan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20her%20career%2C%20Culberg%20said