cation%2C%20and%20the%20postponement%20of%20the%20NEET-PG%20just%20a%20day%20before%20it%20was%20to%20be%20held%20-%20all%20these%20point%20at%20gaps%20in%20how%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20(NTA)%20worked%2C%20sources%20have%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NEET-PG%20is%20administered%20by%20the%20National%20Board%20of%20Examinations%20under%20the%20Health%20Ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEducation%20ministry%20sources%20said%20the%20government%20is%20looking%20to%20implement%20every%20critical%20reform%20in%20the%20NTA%20before%20the%20next%20cycle%20of%20exams%20begin%20in%202025.%20They%20said%20the%20NTA%20will%20also%20see%20whether%20NEET%20can%20be%20held%20multiple%20times%20or%20just%20once%20a%20year%2C%20apart%20from%20chalking%20out%20best%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20replaced%20the%20NTA%20Director%20General%20Subodh%20Kumar%20Singh%20with%20retired%20Indian%20Administration%20Service%20(IAS)%20officer%20Pradeep%20Singh%20Kharola%2C%20a%20move%20which%20sources%20said%20sought%20to%20save%20the%20NTA's%20credibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20students'%20confidence%20in%20the%20NTA%20had%20diminished%20following%20the%20controversies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20NTA%20failed%20to%20assure%20candidates.%20There%20has%20been%20no%20provision%20to%20give%20grace%20marks.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20time%20grace%20marks%20have%20been%20given%20to%20candidates.%20As%20per%20the%20rules%2C%20the%20candidates%20should%20have%20been%20given%20extra%20time%20if%20there%20was%20some%20time%20loss.%20And%20then%20the%20grace%20marking%20was%20done%20through%20the%20odd%20method%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20Education%20Ministry%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NTA%20had%20awarded%20grace%20marks%20to%201%2C564%20candidates%20due%20to%20loss%20of%20exam%20time.%20It%20said%20it%20followed%20the%20same%20normalisation%20formula%20that%20had%20been%20approved%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20the%20CLAT%20in%202018%2C%