bered%20the%20locals%20in%20these%20villages.%20The%20Myanmar%20nationals%20are%20actually%20refugees%20who%20fled%20from%20the%20fighting%20between%20the%20junta%20forces%20and%20pro-democracy%20insurgents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Myanmar%20nationals%20being%20sheltered%20in%20the%20six%20Maring%20Naga%20villages%20(Saibol%2C%20Moirengthel%2C%20Chanringphai%2C%20Lamlong%20Khunou%2C%20Choktong%2C%20and%20Satang)%2C%20numbering%20about%201%2C428%20(only%20those%20whose%20biometrics%20were%20captured)%2C%20have%20outnumbered%20the%20local%20residents%2C%20which%20is%20of%20great%20concern%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20MSU%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MSU's%20statement%20comes%20over%20a%20month%20after%20Naga%20People's%20Front%20(NPF)%20MLA%20Leishiyo%20Keishing%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20Manipur%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Biren%20Singh%20on%20May%209%20alleged%20Myanmar%20nationals%20living%20in%20shelter%20homes%20in%20eight%20villages%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmyanmar-nationals-in-shelter-homes-outnumber-locals-in-8-villages-manipur-mla-5655993%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bhave%20outnumbered%26quot%3B%20locals%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20raising%20feelings%20of%20insecurity%20among%20the%20locals%20amid%20the%20ethnic%20tension%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20the%20claims%20by%20the%20NPF%20MLA%2C%20BJP%20MLA%20Paolienlal%20Haokip%20had%20told%20NDTV%20that%20if%20the%20data%20quoted%20by%20Mr%20Keishing%20was%20correct%2C%20then%20it%20clearly%20indicated%20the%20number%20of%20refugees%20coming%20from%20war-torn%20Myanmar%20was%20highest%20in%20Ukhrul%20and%20Kamjong%20districts.%20Mr%20Haokip%20had%20alleged%20the%20state%20government%20focussed%20only%20on%20Kuki%20villages%2C%20and%20not%20the%20villages%20where%20tribes%20other%20than%20Kukis%20live.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Ftbk522t8_manipur-illegal-immigrants_625x300_02_May_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MSU%20alleged%20Rilram%20Area%20Maring%20Organisation%20(RAMO)%20have%20been%20targeted%20after%20a%20survey%20by%20its%20volunteers%20in%20the%20border%20district%20found%20refugees%20from%20Myanmar%20allegedly%20building%20houses%20without%20informing%20the%20state%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Union%20demands%20an%20end%20to%20their%20intimidation%20to%20village%20leaders%20and%20dissemination%20of%20misleading%20reports%2C%20particularly%20those%20unjustly%20targeting%20RAMO%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20MSU%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Assam%20Rifles%2C%20which%20guards%20the%20border%20in%20this%20region%2C%20had%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20local%20media%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fassam-rifles-refutes-maring-tribe-bodys-allegations-on-illegal-immigrants-in-manipur-5925614%5C%22%3Edenied%20the%20existence%20of%20such%20%26quot%3Billegal%20settlements%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20alleged%20by%20RAMO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20refugees%20have%20indeed%20taken%20shelter%20in%20that%20area%20due%20to%20the%20war-like%20situation%20in%20Myanmar%3B%20however%2C%20they%20are%20immediately%20repatriated%20as%20the%20security%20situation%20improves%20across%20the%20Indo-Myanmar%20border%2C%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20had%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20the%20accommodation%20arrangements%20for%20the%20refugees%20consist%20of%20self-help%2C%20bare%20essential%20thatched%20huts%20with%20polythene%20covers%2C%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20said%2C%20adding%20the%20state%20administration%20is%20fully%20aware%20of%20the%20presence%20of%20refugees%20in%20the%20area%20and%20has%20also%20collected%20their%20biometric%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecurity%20sources%20have%20refuted%20the%20MSU's%20allegations%20that%20security%20forces%20have%20been%20hindering%20movement%20of%20commuters%20in%20the%20Maring%20tribe's%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERAMO%20on%20Tuesday%20had%20said%20it%20sent%20out%20volunteers%20to%20check%20their%20villages%20near%20border%20pillar%20numbers%2082%20to%2089%2C%20following%20reports%20of%20a%20significant%20number%20of%20Myanmar%20refugees%20pouring%20into%20Maring%20tribe's%20areas%20in%20Tengnoupal%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERAMO%20said%20they%20told%20the%20authorities%20they%20found%20a%20considerable%20presence%20of%20Myanmar%20refugees%20building%20houses%20and%20other%20structures.%20The%20areas%20RAMO%20volunteers%20visited%20were%20Chanringphai%2C%20Choktong%2C%20N%20Satang%2C%20and%20Sangtong%20villages%20under%20Lamlong%20Khunou%20circle.%20Village%20chiefs%20in%20the%20area%20have%20complained%20they%20were%20no%20longer%20able%20to%20manage%20the%20influx%20of%20refugees%20from%20Myanmar%2C%20the%20RAMO%20volunteers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAs%20highlighted%20by%20Kamjong%20MLA%20Mr%20Leishiyo%20Keishing%2C%20the%20total%20number%20of%20illegal%20influx%20touched%205800%20in%20the%20area%20of%20Kamjong%20District%2C%20outnumbering%20the%20local%20populace%2C%20detection%20of%20such%20illegal%20migrants%20along%20with%20capturing%20of%20biometrics%20has%20been%20done%20for%20more%20than%205100%20of%20them....%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F08mIVhEWTn%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F08mIVhEWTn%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Rajkumar%20Imo%20Singh%20(%40imosingh)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fimosingh%2Fstatus%2F1790011199192789427%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%2013%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20Naga%20civil%20bodies%20and%20organisations%20in%20Manipur%20last%20week%20asked%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20to%20repatriate%20%26quot%3Billegal%20Myanmar%20immigrants%26quot%3B.%20After