%20Party%20Trade%20Charges%20Over%20Alleged%20Land%20Grab%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20YSRCP%20party%20office%20under%20construction%20in%20Guntur%20district%20on%20Saturday%20and%20notices%20to%20two%20more%20YSRCP%20offices%20in%20Visakhapatnam%20for%20allegedly%20being%20illegal%2C%20the%20ruling%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP)%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20says%20similar%20violations%20are%20being%20discovered%20across%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYSRCP%20president%20YS%20Jaganmohan%20Reddy%20has%20called%20it%20vendetta%20politics%20and%20said%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20near-complete%20building%20showed%20how%20the%20regime%20is%20going%20to%20be%20over%20the%20next%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20state%20minister%20and%20TDP%20general%20secretary%20Nara%20Lokesh%20posted%20on%20X%20pictures%20of%20YSRCP%20offices%20being%20built%20at%20various%20places%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20alleged%20the%20previous%20government%20led%20by%20Mr%20Reddy%20allotted%2042%20acres%20in%2026%20districts%20for%2033%20years%20for%20a%20nominal%20lease%20of%20Rs%201%2C000%20per%20acre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJagan%2C%20is%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20your%20grandfather%20Raja%20Reddy's%20property%3F%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Lokesh%2C%20who%20is%20the%20son%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20TDP%20president%20N%20Chandrababu%20Naidu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Lokesh%20alleged%20Mr%20Reddy%20was%20building%20%26quot%3Bpalaces%26quot%3B%20with%20Rs%20500%20crore%20%26quot%3Blooted%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20these%2042%20acres%20worth%20more%20than%20Rs%20600%20crore%2C%20grabbed%20for%20your%20land%20thirst%2C%204%2C200%20poor%20can%20be%20given%20house%20sites.%20With%20Rs%20500%20crore%20being%20spent%20on%20your%20luxurious%20palaces%2C%20houses%20can%20be%20constructed%20for%2025%2C000%20poor%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Lokesh%20posted%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20this%20madness%20for%20palaces%3F%20Is%20there%20no%20end%20to%20your%20thirst%20for%20money%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TDP%20alleged%20Mr%20Reddy%20built%20%26quot%3Bpalaces%26quot%3B%20for%20himself%20in%20nine%20cities%20including%20Hyderabad%20and%20Bengaluru%2C%20and%20he%20was%20now%20building%20%26quot%3Bpalaces%26quot%3B%20for%20his%20party%20offices%20with%20public%20money%20and%20without%20approvals%20from%20the%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TDP%20alleged%20that%2042.24%20acres%20of%20government%20land%20in%2026%20districts%20were%20allotted%20for%20YSRCP's%20offices%20for%20a%2033-year%20lease%20at%20a%20nominal%20cost%20of%20Rs%201%2C000%20per%20acre.%20%26quot%3BThe%20value%20of%20the%2042.24%20acres%20is%20Rs%20688%20crore%20while%20more%20than%20Rs%20500%20crore%20of%20public%20money%20is%20being%20spent%20to%20build%20these%20palaces%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20TDP%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TDP%20claimed%20that%20permissions%20were%20not%20taken%20for%20YSRCP%20offices%2C%20except%20in%20Prakasam%20district.%20The%20YSRCP%20says%20between%202014%20and%202019%2C%20the%20TDP%20government%20had%20allotted%20government%20land%20in%2010%20districts%20on%20lease%20for%2033%20to%2099%20years%20for%20Rs%201%2C000%20per%20acre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20do%20it%2C%20it's%20politics%20and%20if%20we%20do%2C%20it's%20land%20grabbing%2C%26quot%3B%20reads%20a%20post%20on%20YSRCP's%20official%20handle%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BHave%20you%20not%20issued%20a%20GO%20and%20built%20TDP%20offices%20across%20the%20state%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20Opposition%20party%20asked.%20It%20alleged%20the%20land%20for%20NTR%20Bhavan%20(TDP%20office)%20in%20Hyderabad%20was%20also%20allotted%20in%20the%20same%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20YSRCP%20said%20if%20the%20previous%20government%20had%20resorted%20to%20a%20similar%20act%2C%20no%20TDP%20office%20would%20have%20remained%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20under-construction%20office%20building%20of%20YSRCP%20at%20Seethanagaram%20of%20Tadepalli%20Mandal%20in%20Guntur%20district%20was%20demolished%20by%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Capital%20Region%20Development%20Authority%20(APCRDA)%20and%20Mangalagiri%20Tadepalli%20Municipal%20Corporation%20(MTMC)%20authorities%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20APCRDA%20had%20issued%20notice%20on%20June%2010%20to%20the%20YSRCP%20for%20taking%20up%20construction%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Billegally%20occupied%26quot%3B%20land%20of%20870.40%20sqm%20within%20the%20boat%20yard%20compound%20of%20the%20irrigation%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20APCRDA%20said%20the%20previous%20government%20leased%20two%20acres%2C%20which%20was%20a%20boatyard%20and%20water%20body%2C%20to%20the%20YSRCP%20on%20a%20lease%20of%20Rs%201%2C000%20per%20acre%2C%20per%20annum%20for%2033%20years%20for%20their%20party%20office.%20It%20was%20also%20alleged%20the%20party%20undertook%20construction%20without%20getting%20approvals%20from%20the%20irrigation%20department%20and%20the%20MTMC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20YSRCP%20had%20filed%20a%20writ%20petition%20in%20the%20high%20court%2C%20seeking%20orders%20to%20the%20CRDA%20and%20MTMC%20not%20to%20take%20any%20coercive%20action%20against%20the%20building%20structure%2C%20until%20hearing%20was%20completed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClaiming%20that%20the%20high%20court%20had%20ordered%20a%20halt%20on%20any%20demolition%20activity%2C%20the%20Opposition%20has%20slammed%20the%20government%20for%20violating%20the%20court's%20order.%20YSRCP%20plans%20to%20approach%20the%20court%20on%20Monday%2C%20seeking%20criminal%20action%20against%20those%20who%20carried%20out%20the%20demolition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Town%20Planning%20wing%20of%20the%20Greater%20Visakhapatnam%20Municipal%20Corporation%20(GVMC)%20has%20issued%20show%20cause%20notices%20to%20YSRCP%20seeking%20an%20explanation%20over%20%26quot%3Bunauthorised%20construction%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20party%20offices%20at%20Yendada%20and%20Anakapalli.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20alleged%20YSRCP%20proceeded%20with%20the%20construction%20of%20G%2B1%20building%20over%20a%20stretch%20of%20two%20acres%20at%20Yendada%20without%20permission%20from%20the%20authorities.%20Similarly%2C%20construction%20of%20the%20YSRCP%20office%20at%20Anakapalli%20was%20taken%20up%20allegedly%20without%20approvals%2C%20the%20government%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYSRCP%20leader%20and%20former%20minister%20Gudivada%20Amarnath%20removed%20the%20notice%20pasted%20on%20the%20office%20at%20Yedanda.%20He%20said%20the%20land%20was%20allotted%20in%202022%20and%20construction%20began%20in%20March%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20around%20Rs%2013%20lakh%20and%20Rs%2030%20lakh%20were%20paid%20to%20the%20government%20as%20taxes%20for%20plan%20approvals%20for%20the%20party%20offices%20at%20Yendada%20and%20Anakapalli%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719164460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F4qol01pg_jagan-naidu_650x400_10_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fandhra-pradesh-news%2Fjagan-reddy-vs-c-naidus-party-trade-charges-over-alleged-government-land-grab-5954181%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20YSRCP%20party%20office%20under%20construction%20in%20Guntur%20district%20on%20Saturday%20and%20notices%20to%20two%20more%20YSRCP%20offices%20in%20Visakhapatnam%20for%20allegedly%20being%20illegal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fandhra-pradesh-news%2Fjagan-reddy-vs-c-naidus-party-trade-charges-over-alleged-government-land-grab-5954181%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fandhra-pradesh-news%2Fjagan-reddy-vs-c-naidus-party-trade-charges-over-alleged-government-land-grab-5954181%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fandhra-pradesh-news%2Fjagan-reddy-vs-c-naidus-party-trade-charges-over-alleged-