%20for%20Group%201%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20(4%20points%2C%202%20games%3B%20NRR%20%2B2.4)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20co%2C%20the%20equation%20is%20simple.%20Beat%20Australia.%20That%20would%20make%20the%20Afghanistan%20vs%20Bangladesh%20game%20irrelevant%20to%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20them%20to%20miss%20out%20on%20semi-finals%20from%20this%20position%20is%20highly%20unlikely%2C%20but%20not%20impossible.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20can%20miss%20out%20if%20both%20Australia%20and%20Afghanistan%20win%20by%20big%20margins.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAustralia%20need%20to%20beat%20India%20by%2041%20runs%20to%20go%20above%20them%20on%20Net%20Run%20Rate%20(NRR)%2C%20while%20Afghanistan%20will%20have%20to%20win%20against%20Bangladesh%20by%20at%20least%2083%20runs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20case%20of%20a%20washout%2C%20India%20will%20go%20through%20as%20no%20other%20team%20can%20achieve%20five%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAustralia%20(2%20points%2C%202%20games%3B%20NRR%20%2B0.22)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20it%20to%20the%20semi-finals%2C%20Australia%20need%20to%20beat%20India%20first.%20Then%20the%20side%20would%20hope%20Bangladesh%20to%20beat%20Afghanistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20Australia%20lose%20their%20final%20game%20by%20a%20narrow%20margin%2C%20they%20will%20be%20in%20the%20semis%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20case%2C%20Australia%20will%20need%20Bangladesh%20to%20beat%20Afghanistan%20by%20such%20a%20margin%20that%20the%20two%20teams'%20NRRs%20remains%20lower%20than%20that%20of%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAustralia%20will%20also%20be%20having%20a%20chance%20if%20their%20match%20vs%20India%20is%20abandoned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAustralia%20will%20then%20need%20Bangladesh%20to%20beat%20Afghanistan%20or%20the%20match%20between%20the%20two%20to%20be%20abandoned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAfghanistan%20(2%20points%2C%202%20games%3B%20NRR%20-0.65)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20India%20beat%20Australia%20and%20Bangladesh%20win%20against%20Afghanistan%2C%20three%20teams%20will%20be%20tied%20on%20two%20points%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20case%2C%20NRR%20will%20have%20the%20final%20say.%20Australia%20currently%20have%20a%20better%20net%20run%20rate%20than%20both%20Afghanistan%20and%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Afghanistan%20lose%20by%20one%20run%2C%20Australia%20will%20need%20to%20lose%20by%2031%20for%20their%20net%20run%20rate%20to%20slip%20below%20that%20of%20Afghanistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Australia%20beat%20India%20by%20one%20run%2C%20Afghanistan%20would%20need%20a%2036-run%20margin%20to%20move%20ahead%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20if%20Australia%20win%20off%20the%20final%20ball%20while%20chasing%2C%20Afghanistan%20will%20have%20to%20win%20their%20game%20in%2015.4%20overs%20or%20sooner%20(assuming%20the%20first-innings%20score%20is%20160).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20case%20of%20a%20washout%2C%20Afghanistan%20would%20need%20a%20favour%20from%20India%20in%20their%20game%20against%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBangladesh%20(0%20points%2C%202%20matches%3B%20-2.48)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBangladesh%20have%20the%20worst%20net%20run%20rate%20in%20the%20group%20and%20sit%20bottom%20with%20zero%20points.%20However%2C%20they%20still%20have%20an%20outside%20chance%20to%20make%20it%20to%20the%20semi-finals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20must%20win%20by%2031%20runs%20for%20their%20NRR%20to%20sneak%20ahead%20of%20Afghanistan's%2C%20and%20also%20hope%20that%20Australia%20lose%20by%20at%20least%2055%20runs%2C%20to%20finish%20second.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20defeat%20or%20a%20washout%20in%20either%20of%20those%20games%20will%20end%20their%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1