%20evening.%20The%20NTA%20had%20opened%20seven%20exam%20centres%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Meghalaya%2C%20and%20Chandigarh%2C%20a%20Union%20Territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%F0%9F%94%B4%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FJustIn%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23JustIn%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20NEET-UG%202024%20retest%3A%20Only%2052%25%20(813%20out%20of%201563)%20students%20turned%20up%20for%20the%20retest%20today.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FJZzsxmDh8c%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FJZzsxmDh8c%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20NDTV%20(%40ndtv)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fndtv%2Fstatus%2F1804865371603640719%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2023%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBelow%20is%20the%20list%20of%20how%20many%20students%20gave%20the%20retest%2C%20how%20many%20skipped%2C%20and%20the%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChandigarh%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%202%20eligible%2C%20both%20absent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChhattisgarh%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20602%20eligible%2C%20311%20absent%2C%20291%20took%20retest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGujarat%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%201%20eligible%2C%20and%20the%20student%20turned%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHaryana%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20494%20eligible%2C%20207%20absent%2C%20287%20took%20retest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMeghalaya%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E464%20eligible%2C%20230%20absent%2C%20234%20took%20retest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20retest%20was%20held%20on%20a%20day%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20filed%20a%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20in%20connection%20with%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20medical%20entrance%20exam%20NEET-UG%20held%20on%20May%205.%20The%20CBI%20filed%20the%20case%20following%20a%20complaint%20from%20the%20Education%20Ministry%20amid%20protests%20and%20litigation%20by%20students%20for%20a%20probe%20into%20paper%20leak%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20the%20ministry%20alleged%20in%20the%20complaint%2C%20now%20part%20of%20the%20FIR%2C%20that%20%26quot%3Bcertain%20isolated%20incidents%26quot%3B%20happened%20in%20a%20few%20states%20during%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20examination.%20Giving%20top%20priority%20to%20the%20case%2C%20the%20CBI%20has%20formed%20special%20teams%20that%20are%20on%20their%20way%20to%20Godhra%20and%20Patna%2C%20where%20cases%20of%20question%20paper%20leaks%20have%20been%20filed%20by%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20will%20take%20over%20the%20investigation%20of%20the%20cases%20filed%20by%20the%20police%20in%20Gujarat%20and%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESixty-three%20candidates%20were%20debarred%20from%20all%20over%20the%20country%20over%20malpractices%20during%20the%20NEET-UG%2C%20the%20NTA%20said.%20They%20include%2017%20from%20Bihar%2C%20and%2030%20from%20Godhra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20role%20of%20officials%2C%20if%20any%2C%20connected%20with%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20examination%20and%20also%20into%20the%20entire%20gamut%20of%20events%2C%20and%20the%20larger%20conspiracy%20will%20also%20be%20under%20the%20scanner%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20separate%20matter%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20sought%20responses%20from%20the%20Centre%2C%20the%20NTA%20and%20others%20on%20various%20petitions%2C%20including%20those%20seeking%20cancellation%20of%20the%20NEET-UG%202024%20exam%20and%20a%20court-monitored%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20also%20halted%20proceedings%20on%20similar%20petitions%20in%20various%20high%20courts.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719153060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-03%2F1lbvjrv8_exam-generic-_625x300_15_March_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F750-of-1-563-students-skipped-neet-ug-retest-exam-body-nta-5952815%2