Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPer%20Swiss%20law%20procedures%2C%20the%20lower%20court's%20judgment%20is%20rendered%20ineffective%20and%20inoperative%20as%20the%20presumption%20of%20innocence%20is%20paramount%20until%20and%20unless%20a%20final%20judgment%20by%20the%20highest%20adjudicating%20authority%20is%20enforced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20most%20serious%20of%20the%20charges%2C%20human%20trafficking%2C%20against%20them%20were%20completely%20dismissed%20by%20the%20court%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20may%20be%20noted%20that%20the%20case%20has%20no%20complainants%20left%20anymore%20and%20they%20had%20declared%20in%20the%20court%20that%20they%20were%20led%20into%20signing%20statements%20that%20they%20didn't%20even%20understand.%20They%20had%20neither%20intended%20to%20nor%20initiated%20such%20proceedings.%20All%20of%20them%20further%20testified%20that%20the%20four%20Hinduja%20family%20members%20treated%20them%20with%20'respect%2C%20dignity%20and%20like%20family.'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20four%20family%20members%20have%20full%20faith%20in%20the%20Swiss%20judicial%20process%20and%20remain%20confident%20that%20the%20truth%20will%20prevail.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719152880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Ftg30klj_hindujas-afp_625x300_22_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhindujas-not-imprisoned-human-trafficking-charges-dismissed-spokesperson-5953187%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Four%20members%20of%20Britain's%20richest%20family%2C%20the%20Hindujas%2C%20on%20Sunday%20said%20they%20have%20not%20been%20subjected%20to%20any%20imprisonment%2C%20conviction%2C%20sentence%20or%20detention.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhindujas-not-imprisoned-human-trafficking-charges-dismissed-spokesperson-5953187%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.or