n%20save%20you%20lakhs%20on%20electricity%20bills%20and%20prove%20a%20great%20investment%20in%20the%20long%20run.%20Media%20professional%20Shalini%20whose%20%E2%80%98Raison%20D%E2%80%99etre%E2%80%99%20is%20a%20beautiful%20homestay%20in%20Manali%2C%20recognised%20this%20potential%20early%20on.%20She%20along%20with%20her%20husband%20Nitin%20Beri%20are%20advocates%20of%20sustainable%20living%20and%20were%20keen%20that%20the%20homestay%20be%20a%20symbol%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShalini%20emphasises%20that%20they%20run%20their%20operations%20entirely%20on%20solar%20power%20and%20have%20a%20solar%20system%20in%20place%20that%20generates%20electricity%20on%20which%20the%20entire%20home%20runs.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20on%20days%20when%20there%E2%80%99s%20as%20little%20as%2030%20percent%20sunlight%2C%20the%20system%20works%20efficiently.%20Additionally%2C%20any%20excess%20energy%20generated%20during%20the%20day%20is%20stored%20in%20batteries%2C%20which%20we%20then%20use%20for%20power%20backup%20when%20needed%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Nitin.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReach%20out%20to%20them%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fraisondetremanali%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Solar%20for%20street%20shops%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FV_X4-pszhBY%3Fsi%3DGx2Wekg4dIYkjvjL%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20speak%2C%20an%20energy%20revolution%20is%20steadily%20brewing%20in%20the%20country%20and%20across%20the%20world.%20According%20to%20data%20by%20Rystad%20Energy%2C%20India%20installed%20a%20record%207.1%20gigawatts%20(GW)%20capacity%20renewable%20energy%20sources%20in%20March%2C%20helping%20the%20country%20reach%20its%20highest-ever%20annual%20installed%20capacity%20of%2018.5%20GW%20in%20FY24.%20And%20this%20marked%20change%20is%20being%20embraced%20across%20sectors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHave%20you%20ever%20avoided%20buying%20produce%20after%20dark%20for%20fear%20of%20not%20being%20able%20to%20notice%20signs%20of%20spoilage%3F%20You%20aren%E2%80%99t%20the%20only%20one.%20But%20when%20this%20practice%20is%20extrapolated%20to%20the%20masses%2C%20it%20has%20an%20impact%20on%20the%20businesses%20run%20by%20street%20vendors.%20They%20find%20themselves%20in%20a%20rush%20to%20sell%20their%20produce%20before%20dusk%2C%20and%20are%20anxious%20about%20the%20produce%20that%20gets%20left%20behind%20as%20it%20will%20be%20discarded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Aakarsh%20Shamanur%2C%20a%20Bengaluru-based%20social%20entrepreneur%20noticed%20this%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20bring%20a%20change%20in%20this%20niche%20segment%20using%20the%20power%20of%20solar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20venture%20%E2%80%98Be%20Po-Lite%E2%80%99%20aims%20at%20being%20%E2%80%98a%20ray%20of%20light%E2%80%99%20for%20women%20street%20vendors%20who%20can%20now%20use%20the%203W%20solar-powered%20portable%20lamps%20to%20run%20their%20stalls%20even%20after%20the%20sun%20goes%20down.%20The%20women%20are%20encouraged%20to%20take%20the%20lamps%20home%2C%20use%20them%20for%20cooking%2C%20and%20to%20help%20their%20children%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20multi-purpose%20innovation!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReach%20out%20to%20him%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fbepolite_city%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Solar%20power%20for%20making%20%3Cem%3Erotis%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20article%20posted%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EMinistry%20of%20New%20and%20Renewable%20Energy%3C%2Fem%3E%20narrated%20the%20story%20of%20two%20women%2C%20Jos