00w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-power-1718978521-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-power-1718978521-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-353915%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETailoring%20is%20one%20of%20the%20home-run%20businesses%20that%20is%20starting%20to%20see%20solar%20power%20being%20integrated%20into%20scale%20production%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Representational%20image%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20people%20in%20the%20rural%20hinterland%20of%20India%20have%20time%20and%20again%20shown%20a%20display%20of%20market%20muscle%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20innovation.%20One%20such%20village%20where%20this%20is%20evident%20is%20Maganpur%2C%20a%20hamlet%20near%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20Ramgarh%20district.%20While%20coal%20mines%20dot%20the%20landscape%20of%20this%20hamlet%2C%20clean%20energy%20is%20sprouting%20in%20many%20of%20its%20homes%3B%20the%20dichotomy%20is%20evident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20article%20published%20by%20%3Cem%3EScroll%20%3C%2Fem%3Espanned%20the%20expanse%20of%20the%20homes%20in%20Maganpur%2C%20delving%20into%20the%20businesses%20that%20are%20operated%20within%20the%20four%20walls.%20As%20they%20discovered%20it%20was%20majorly%20tailoring%20businesses%20that%20were%20being%20run.%20The%20article%20spotlighted%20the%20story%20of%20a%20woman%20Kaniz%20Fatima%20who%20has%20been%20engaged%20in%20sewing%20for%20years.%20She%20and%20her%20husband%20made%20only%20a%20meagre%20Rs%20150%20per%20day%20through%20their%20work%2C%20as%20per%20the%20article.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%202020%2C%20when%20a%20foundation%20stepped%20in%20to%20help%20them%20secure%20a%20bank%20loan%20of%20Rs%2015%2C000%2C%20which%20enabled%20them%20to%20install%20solar%20panels%20on%20their%20roof%2C%20their%20life%20changed%20for%20the%20better.%20Their%20earnings%20