0clerk%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20Ashish%20%E2%80%94%20a%20graduate%20from%20IIT%20Kharagpur%20%E2%80%94%20quit%20a%20well-paying%20job%20to%20pursue%20a%20career%20in%20civil%20service.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20said%20that%20I%20ruined%20my%20life%20by%20setting%20out%20on%20a%20difficult%20path%20when%20I%20could%20have%20established%20a%20good%20career%20in%20the%20corporate%20world%20and%20settled%20abroad%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20getting%20affected%20by%20the%20taunts%2C%20the%2029-year-old%20remained%20determined%20and%20today%20has%20fulfilled%20his%20dream.%20After%20four%20failed%20attempts%2C%20he%20cleared%20the%20examination%20and%20secured%20an%20impressive%20All%20India%20Rank%20of%208%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAny%20student%20can%20clear%20this%20exam%20irrespective%20of%20their%20academic%20background.%20You%20do%20not%20need%20to%20be%20extraordinary.%20The%20only%20key%20to%20ace%20this%20exam%20is%20to%20be%20dedicated%20and%20consistent%20in%20efforts.%20If%20you%20have%20perseverance%2C%20no%20one%20can%20stop%20you%20from%20achieving%20success%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20opines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Ashish-1-1718972736.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ashish%20secured%20an%20impressive%20All%20India%20Rank%20of%208%20in%202023.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Ashish-1-1718972736.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Ashish-1-1718972736-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Ashish-1-1718972736-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Ashish-1-1718972736-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Ashish-1-1718972736-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-353826%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAshish%20secured%20an%20impressive%20All%20India%20Rank%20of%208%20in%202023.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20sat%20down%20with%20the%20IAS%20officer%20to%20trace%20his%20triumphant%20UPSC%20journey%20and%20share%20the%20mistakes%20and%20learnings%20that%20led%20to%20success%20after%20four%20failed%20attempts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETry%2C%20try%2C%20until%20you%20succeed%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20his%20graduation%2C%20Ashish%20worked%20for%20a%20year%20in%20Gurugram.%20It%20was%20during%20the%20job%20that%20he%20understood%20his%20true%20calling.%20%E2%80%9CI%20realised%20I%20did%20not%20belong%20in%20the%20corporate%20world%20and%20I%20needed%20to%20be%20somewhere%20else.%20Civil%20services%20provide%20social%20connect%2C%20diversity%20in%20work%2C%20and%20power%20to%20make%20a%20change.%20People-centricity%20was%20a%20major%20driving%20force.%20I%20felt%20administration%20was%20a%20way%20to%20lead%20a%20purpose-driven%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20he%20quit%20the%20job%20and%20started%20preparing%20for%20UPSC.%20With%2010%20months%20of%20preparation%2C%20Ashish%20managed%20to%20clear%20prelims%20in%20his%20very%20first%20attempt.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20focussed%20on%20prelims%20but%20I%20did%20not%20prepare%20for%20Mains%20at%20all.%20I%20was%20in%20a%20celebratory%20mood.%20By%20the%20time%20I%20realised%20I%20needed%20to%20prepare%20for%20Mains%2C%20I%E2%80%99d%20wasted%20a%20month%20and%20had%20just%20two%20months%20left%20for%20preparation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20expected%2C%20Ashish%20failed%20the%20Mains%20in%202018.%20%E2%80%9CI%20knew%20that%20my%20preparation%20was%20not%20sufficient%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20motivated%20to%20attempt%20again%20but%20sadly%2C%20he%20failed%20the%20prelims%20in%20the%20second%20attempt%20in%202020.%20In%20his%20third%20attempt%20in%202021%2C%20he%20managed%20to%20clear%20the%20prelims%20but%20missed%20the%20Mains%20cut%20off%20by%2020%20marks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Ashish-2-1718972776.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ashish%20graduated%20from%20IIT%20Kharagpur%20and%20later%20on%20quit%20a%20well-paying%20job%20to%20pursue%20a%20career%20in%20civil%20service.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Ashish-2-1718972776.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Ashish-2-1718972776-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Ashish-2-1718972776-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Ashish-2-1718972776-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Ashish-2-1718972776-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-353827%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAshish%20graduated%20from%20IIT%20Kharagpur%20and%20later%20on%20quit%20a%20well-paying%20job%20to%20pursue%20a%20career%20in%20civil%20service.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20could%20not%20concentrate%20better%20as%20my%20sister%E2%80%99s%20marriage%20was%20just%2015%20days%20before%20the%20exam.%20Being%20a%20brother%2C%20I%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20responsibilities%20to%20cater%20to.%20I%20considered%20this%20failure%20as%20part%20of%20the%20journey%20and%20did%20not%20feel%20discouraged.%20Also%2C%20there%20was%20only%20a%20marginal%20gap%20in%20marks%2C%20so%20I%20could%20try%20one%20more%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESadly%2C%20he%20failed%20in%20prelims%20in%20the%20fourth%20attempt.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20a%20major%20setback%20for%20me.%20I%20was%20disheartened.%20But%20I%20understood%20that%20something%20was%20lacking%20in%20my%20strategy%20because%20of%20which%20I%20was%20either%20failing%20prelims%20or%20Mains%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20did%20wonder%20if%20he%20should%20quit%20preparation%20and%20go%20back%20to%20corporate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20Ashish%20was%20motivated%20to%20give%20one%20last%20try.%20He%20appeared%20for%20his%20fifth%20attempt%20and%20finally%20achieved%20success%20%E2%80%94%20securing%20an%20impressive%20AIR%208!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFive%20ultimate%20tips%20to%20guarantee%20success%20in%20UPSC%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshish%20shares%20how%20he%20changed%20his%20strategy%20in%20the%20fifth%20attempt%20to%20clear%20UPSC%20CSE%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Be%20Consistent%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20the%20fifth%20attempt%2C%20I%20knew%20what%20I%20needed%20to%20study%2C%20but%20I%20lacked%20consistency.%20If%20you%20have%20decided%20to%20become%20a%20civil%20servant%2C%20you%20must%20work%20hard%20consistently.%20So%2C%20if%20you%20study%20for%20four%20days%20and%20then%20rest%20for%20the%20next%20four%20days%2C%20then%20you%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20achieve%20success.%20It%E2%80%99s%20better%20to%20study%20all%20eight%20days%20even%20though%20for%20fewer%20hours%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20How%20to%20read%20the%20newspaper%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshish%20says%20his%20day%20started%20by%20reading%20the%20newspaper%20%E2%80%94%20either%20The%20Hindu%20or%20The%20Indian%20Express.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20read%20the%20newspaper%20for%20about%20an%20hour.%20The%20strategy%20to%20read%20the%20newspaper%20should%20be%20different%20for%20aspirants.%20Usually%2C%20people%20look%20for%20%3Cem%3Emasala%20%3C%2Fem%3Enews%20but%20as%20an%20aspirant%2C%20I%20looked%20for%20topics%20related%20to%20constitution%2C%20environment%2C%20or%20economy.%20A%20few%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F337399%2Fbihar-ias-officer-anshuman-raj-cracked-upsc-cse-without-coaching-success-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecoaching%20centres%20%3C%2Fa%3Elike%20Vajiram%20also%20publish%20important%20news%20items%20on%20their%20social%20media%20pages%2C%20mark%20those%20in%20the%20newspaper%20and%20read%20about%20them%20in%20detail%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReading%20the%20newspaper%20daily%20widens%20your%20thought%20process.%20%E2%80%9CSuppose%20there%20is%20an%20editorial%20on%20international%20relations%20between%20India%20and%20China%2C%20journalists%20take%20information%20from%20history%20and%20other%20sources%20to%20compile%20a%20detailed%20piece.%20This%20gives%20you%20an%20idea%20on%20how%20to%20broaden%20your%20thinking%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Ashish-_11zon-1718972552.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22It%20was%20in%20his%20fifth%20attempt%20that%20Ashish%20finally%20achieved%20success.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Ashish-_11zon-1718972552.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Ashish-_11zon-1718972552-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-medi