ed%2C%20in%20her%20own%20words%2C%20was%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9Cpassion%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20search%20for%20her%20passion%20in%20life%20took%20her%20to%20several%20places%20before%20she%20found%20it%20in%20helping%20others.%20Currently%2C%20she%20is%20the%20founder%20of%20Social%20Town%2C%20a%20non-profit%20organisation%20that%20enables%20and%20empowers%20changemakers%20and%20NGOs%20with%20connections%2C%20opportunities%20and%20knowledge%20fostering%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F336971%2Fcourse-in-social-impact-for-changemakers-sp-jain-institute-post-graduate-programme-in-development-management%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esocial%20development.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThink%20of%20it%20as%20a%20social%20media%20platform%20for%20changemakers%20and%20aspiring%20social%20workers.%20The%20organisation%20helps%20you%20connect%20with%20other%20changemakers%20and%20helps%20you%20find%20the%20right%20resources.%20It%20also%20helps%20you%20raise%20funds%20and%20get%20volunteers%20for%20your%20initiative%2C%E2%80%9D%20Neenu%20shares%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20her%20journey%20from%20looking%20for%20her%20passion%20to%20becoming%20a%20social%20entrepreneur%20who%20has%20helped%20over%206%2C000%20stakeholders%20including%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F334179%2Fteenage-changemakers-of-india-children-founders-of-startups-ngos-inspiring%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echangemakers%2C%20NGOs%20and%20corporates%2C%20bring%20social%20change%20%3C%2Fa%3Eby%20raising%20funds%2C%20securing%20the%20right%20connections%20and%20reaching%20the%20people%20who%20need%20help.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EChoosing%20the%20road%20less%20taken%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaised%20in%20Kerala%2C%20Neenu%20was%20not%20sure%20what%20she%20wanted%20to%20do%2C%20so%20she%20decided%20to%20go%20for%20a%20professional%20degree.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20that%20time%2C%20I%20was%20not%20sure%20what%20to%20take%20up%20in%20college%2C%20so%20I%20went%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F343321%2Frahul-arepaka-harvested-robotics-hyderabad-ai-startup-laser-weeder-robot-help-farmers-earn-more%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eahead%20with%20engineering%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20even%20went%20on%20to%20get%20a%20masters%20in%20the%20same%20field%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20Neenu%20was%20among%20her%20peers%20who%20were%20passionate%20about%20engineering%2C%20she%20realised%20that%20she%20was%20a%20misfit%20in%20the%20group.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20realised%20how%20I%20was%20not%20here%20because%20of%20my%20passion%20but%20just%20for%20a%20degree.%20The%20crisis%20of%20not%20knowing%20what%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20with%20my%20life%20kicked%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20even%20got%20placed%20at%20an%20MNC%20in%20the%20third%20year%20of%20my%20college%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20it%20was%20a%20period%20of%20recession%2C%20and%20the%20company%20postponed%20my%20joining%20date.%20So%2C%20I%20started%20my%20career%20as%20a%20lecturer%20in%20a%20small%20engineering%20college.%20When%20I%20began%20working%20there%2C%20I%20quickly%20realised%20that%20the%20students%20were%20extremely%20passionate%20about%20engineering.%20These%20were%20some%20of%20the%20brightest%20minds%20in%20Kerala%2C%20with%20great%20scores%20and%20a%20keen%20interest%20in%20technology%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20I%20felt%20inadequate%20because%20I%20lacked%20professional%20experience%20beyond%20my%20degree%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-i