%20toilet%20flushing%2C%20as%20in%20most%20urban%20areas%2C%2035%25%20of%20the%20freshwater%20supplied%20by%20the%20piped%20water%20system%20is%20wasted%20on%20flushing%20toilets%20every%20day.%20If%20we%20replace%20that%20with%20greywater%2C%20at%20least%2035%20percent%20fresh%20water%20will%20be%20saved%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESetting%20up%20such%20systems%2C%20contrary%20to%20public%20scepticism%20about%20cost%20and%20complexity%2C%20proves%20neither%20difficult%20to%20install%20nor%20expensive%2C%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20basic%20home%20setup%20for%20recycling%201%2C000%20litres%20of%20greywater%20can%20be%20established%20with%20an%20initial%20investment%20of%20approximately%20Rs%2010%2C000.%20Moreover%2C%20larger%20facilities%20like%20housing%20complexes%20or%20educational%20institutions%20can%20implement%20extensive%20recycling%20systems%2C%20with%20costs%20not%20exceeding%20Rs%2020%2C000%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20systems%20not%20only%20recycle%20water%20but%20also%20allow%20for%20percolation%20into%20the%20ground%2C%20aiding%20groundwater%20recharge%20and%20helping%20mitigate%20urban%20heat%20island%20effects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20the%20system%20works%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CGreywater%20filtration%20has%20various%20quality%20standards%20depending%20upon%20the%20reuse%20that%20we%20have%20focusing%20on.%20If%20we%20want%20to%20use%20it%20for%20flushing%20purposes%20we%20can%20have%20a%20simple%20sand%20filter%20which%20is%20a%20natural%20resource.%20However%2C%20if%20we%20want%20to%20use%20it%20for%20mopping%20floors%20or%20washing%20of%20car%20then%20we%20use%20a%205%20Micron%20filter%20which%20will%20filter%20out%20all%20the%20detergent%20and%20harmful%20oil%20from%20the%20water.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInternationally%2C%20nations%20like%20Dubai%20and%20Singapore%20have%20set%20precedents%20by%20filtering%20and%20repurposing%20sewage%20water%20for%20drinking.%